I definitely like the idea of a dream-switching spider, but as already said, the expungement needs help. I do have some questions, though.

Do the sources regain dreams after a set amount of time, or do they never dream again? Are the hallucinations for long periods of time (equal to length of dream?) or just random short bursts? Do the sources remember the recurring dreams taken by the spiders? Is there an antidote for the dream loss?

I think this has a lot of potential to be fleshed out a bit more.







